item.description:
Order (free) tickets via Eventbrite:
http://nhos3a-efbevent.eventbrite.com/

On Saturday 4/6, the NH Objectivist Society will have its 3rd meeting. We will have hors d'oeuvers starting at 7pm followed by a presentation and Q&A with George Lambert. George will be discussing "The fourth branch of government known as Administrative Agencies administer significant influence over free markets and contain within their autonomous authority the ability to be a tool for the implementation of programs that can constrict free market capitalism, stifle innovation, constrain competition, while providing additional funding sources for burdensome regulatory programs and initiatives."


Please BYOB.

53 Riddle Dr.

Bedford, NH 03110

We look forward to seeing you there!
item.name: NH Objectivist Society Meeting
